textBeforeTable: Battlefield 3 preorders, saying 1.5 million have reserved their copies of the upcoming military shooter sequel. They cite an industry analyst as the source of this information: "Sterne Agee analyst Arvind Bhatia has revealed that EA noted the 1.5 million reservations for Battlefield 3 this week. Bhatia noted that the included map pack for BF3 has been a nice incentive for consumers to pre-order."
